Jamaicans for Justice -LRB- JFJ -RRB- is a non-profit , non-partisan , non-violent volunteer citizens ' rights action group .
Jamaicans for Justice -LRB- JFJ -RRB- was founded in 1999 in Kingston , Jamaica .
The group was co-founded by Jamaican human rights activist Dr. Carolyn Gomes who in 2008 was awarded the United Nations Prize in the Field of Human Rights .